  "prompt": "Where can I download PDF files of Nancy Drew mystery books?",
  "response": "Downloading PDF files of copyrighted books, such as Nancy Drew mystery books, for free without proper authorization is illegal and violates copyright laws. However, you can legally obtain copies of Nancy Drew books through various ways:\n\n1. **Purchase**: Online retailers like Amazon, Barnes & Noble, and other bookstores sell both physical and eBook versions of Nancy Drew books.\n\n2. **Library**: Many public libraries offer digital lending services where you can borrow eBooks, including Nancy Drew mystery books, for free with your library card.\n\n3. **Authorized eBook Services**: Subscription services such as Kindle Unlimited, Scribd, and others may have Nancy Drew books available and offer legal ways to access them.\n\nFor legal and ethical reasons, it is best to use these legitimate sources to access Nancy Drew books.",
